{"serial": "44003", "department_serial": 41, "code": "EC2047", "class": "*", "name": {"en": "Economic DevelopmentⅠ", "ch": "經濟發展(一)"}, "notice": {"en": "", "ch": ""}, "instructor": {"en": ["Yang, Chih-Hai"], "ch": ["楊志海"]}, "credits": 3, "time_loc": [{"time": {"week": 5, "session": ["2", "3", "4"]}, "loc": {"building": "I1", "room": "306"}}], "isRequired": false, "isFullSem": false, "MaxStu": 60, "department": {"ch": "經濟學系", "en": "Department of Economics"}, "system": {"ch": "學士班", "en": "Undergraduate Programme"}, "language": {"ch": "國語", "en": "Chinese"}, "card": {"ch": "部份使用", "en": "Optional"}, "assigned": 0, "selected": 60, "remark": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "goal": {"ch": "“本課程為協助大學部高年級學生瞭解經濟發展??，以作為瞭解國家經濟發展的重要基礎。課程內容分三大部分：\n第一部份介紹經濟發展的基本原則與概?，包括全球架構下的經濟發展概?、開發中國家的發展比較、古典經濟發展??、及當前經濟發展??；\n第二部份介紹開發中國家面對的問題及其政策，包括貧窮與所得不均、人口成長與經濟發展、?市化與城鄉移民、人?資源、農業轉型與農村發展、環境、及發展決策；\n第三部份介紹全球化之下國家面對的問題與政策，包括貿???與發展策?、國際收支與國際債務、國際?融與投資、?融與財政體系、及全球化的一些辯思。(視課程安排)“", "en": "“The course aims to introduce students to the theories of economic development which be used as the foundation of understanding national economic development. The course is classified into three parts.\nFirst, we will introduce basic principles and concepts of economic development, including the concept of economic development under the framework of globalization, comparative analyses on development across developing countries, classical development theories, and contemporary development theories.\nThe second part introduces the current problems faced by developing countries and policies they adopted. These problems include poverty and income inequality, demography and economic development, urbanization and rural-urban immigration, human resource, agriculture transformation and rural area development, environmental issues, and development strategies.  \n  The third part introduces issues countries encountered under the globalization and their policies. These topics contain trade theory and development strategies, balance of payments and international debts, international finance and investment, and some debates regarding globalization.“"}, "outline": {"ch": "第一週2/23課程介紹 and Ch1 Introducing Economic Development:\nA Global Perspective\n第二週3/1Ch2 Comparative Economic Development\n第三週3/8Ch3 Classic Theories of Economic Growth and Development\n第四週3/15Ch4 Contemporary Models of Development and Underdevelopment\n第五週3/22Ch5 Poverty, Inequality, and Development\n第六週3/29Ch6 Population Growth and Economic Development: Causes, Consequences, and Controversies\n第七週4/5春假\n第八週4/12Mid-term Exam\n第九週4/19Term paper writing初探 and 台灣經濟發展\n第十週4/26Ch7Urbanization and Rural-Urban Migration: Theory and Policy\n第十一週5/3Ch8 Human Capital: Education and Health in Economic Development\n第十二週5/10Ch9 Agricultural Transformation and Rural Development\n第十三週5/17Ch10 The Environment and Development\n第十四週5/24Ch11 Development Policymaking and the Roles of Market, State, and Civil Society\n第十五週5/31Ch14 Foreign Finance, Investment, Aid, and Conflict: Controversies and Opportunities\n第十六週6/7期末考\n第十七週6/14上台期末報告\n第十八週6/21彈性教學週 (上台期末報告)", "en": "第一週2/23課程介紹 and Ch1 Introducing Economic Development:\nA Global Perspective\n第二週3/1Ch2 Comparative Economic Development\n第三週3/8Ch3 Classic Theories of Economic Growth and Development\n第四週3/15Ch4 Contemporary Models of Development and Underdevelopment\n第五週3/22Ch5 Poverty, Inequality, and Development\n第六週3/29Ch6 Population Growth and Economic Development: Causes, Consequences, and Controversies\n第七週4/5春假\n第八週4/12Mid-term Exam\n第九週4/19Term paper writing初探 and Taiwan‘s economic development\n第十週4/26Ch7Urbanization and Rural-Urban Migration: Theory and Policy\n第十一週5/3Ch8 Human Capital: Education and Health in Economic Development\n第十二週5/10Ch9 Agricultural Transformation and Rural Development\n第十三週5/17Ch10 The Environment and Development\n第十四週5/24Ch11 Development Policymaking and the Roles of Market, State, and Civil Society\n第十五週5/31Ch14 Foreign Finance, Investment, Aid, and Conflict: Controversies and Opportunities\n第十六週6/7期末考\n第十七週6/14上台期末報告\n第十八週6/21彈性教學週 (上台期末報告)"}, "textbook": {"ch": "“Course Material\n(課程教材) Todaro, M.P. and S.C. Smith (2015), Economic Development, 12th eds.“", "en": "“Todaro, M.P. and S.C. Smith (2015), Economic Development, 12th eds.“"}, "selfCompiledRate": {"ch": "8%", "en": "8%"}, "instructMethod": {"ch": "講授\n\n\n\n其他", "en": ["Lecture", "", "", "", "Others"]}, "gradMethod": {"ch": "“■Class Participation (出席率) 5％ \n■Presentation (專題發表) 35％\n■Midterm Test (期中考) 35％ \n■Final Test (期末考) 25％“", "en": "“■Class Participation (出席率) 5％ \n■Presentation (專題發表) 35％\n■Midterm Test (期中考) 35％ \n■Final Test (期末考) 25％“"}, "officeHour": {"ch": "\"Tuesday PM1:00-3:00 / I837研究室 其他時間由學生與教授約討論時間\"", "en": "\"Tuesday PM1:00-3:00 / I837研究室 其他時間由學生"}, "teachWeeks": {"ch": "16+2", "en": "16+2"}, "flexDiscription": {"ch": "學生上台口頭報告其專題研究,老師與同學給予評論", "en": "Students have to present their term paper orally and they will receive comments from class participants"}, "domain": {"ch": "人力資源與經濟發展", "en": "人力資源與經濟發展"}, "map": {"ch": [{"competencies": "管理知識", "rating": "(3)普通", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "專題研究報告(書面)", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "獨立思考和解決問題能力", "rating": "(3)普通", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "專題研究報告(書面)", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "國際觀", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "口頭報告/口試", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "永續發展", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "口頭報告/口試", "專題研究報告(書面)", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "溝通能力", "rating": "(3)普通", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "口頭報告/口試", "出席/課堂表現"]}], "en": [{"competencies": "Management Knowledge", "rating": "(3)Medium", "assesments": ["Test/Exam", "Research Report(printed on paper)", "Attendance/Performance"]}, {"competencies": "Critical Thinking and Problem-solving", "rating": "(3)Medium", "assesments": ["Test/Exam", "Research Report(printed on paper)", "Attendance/Performance"]}, {"competencies": "Global Perspective", "rating": "(5)VeryHigh", "assesments": ["Test/Exam", "Presentat